1- New login page & Settings data
	- Create or open database
		- create: UI to set server settings or offline, and local data path
		- if server: connect and sync
	- list of recent files
	- current file server settings somewhere

2- New login
	- dbi login
		- ldi login, if ok, load user and get uuid
		- if online, rsi login using uuid
		- if ok, set online, else setoffline and show error
  
3- encrypt user data

4- implement all ramobjects
	toJson -> all attributes as JSON, using UUIDs for links
	fromJson
	save method -> call toJson and save to database

5- Sync process
	separate thread: send changes since last sync to server, get new data.
		on demand sync
		periodic sync: Sync interval: option, default, 30s
		get online
		get offline (voluntarily)
